<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>주식부자 모닝 리포트 {{ report_date }}</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#0f1117;font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;color:#e2e8f0;">

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#0f1117;">
<tr><td align="center" style="padding:24px 12px;">

<!-- ── Wrapper ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<table width="620" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width:620px;width:100%;">

  <!-- ── Header ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <tr>
    <td style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1f2e 0%,#0d1526 100%);
               border-radius:12px 12px 0 0;padding:28px 32px;border-bottom:2px solid #2d3a55;">
      <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
        <tr>
          <td>
            <div style="font-size:11px;color:#64748b;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:6px;">
              DAILY MARKET INTELLIGENCE
            </div>
            <div style="font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#f1f5f9;">
              📊 주식부자 모닝 리포트
            </div>
            <div style="font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8;margin-top:4px;">
              {{ report_date }} &nbsp;|&nbsp; {{ report_time }} KST
            </div>
          </td>
          <td align="right" valign="top">
            {% if net_liquidity is not none %}
            <div style="background:#1e2d45;border-radius:8px;padding:10px 16px;text-align:center;">
              <div style="font-size:10px;color:#64748b;letter-spacing:1px;">NET LIQUIDITY</div>
              <div style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:{% if net_liquidity_wow and net_liquidity_wow > 0 %}#34d399{% else %}#f87171{% endif %};">
                ${{ "%.0f"|format(net_liquidity) }}B
              </div>
              {% if net_liquidity_wow is not none %}
              <div style="font-size:11px;color:{% if net_liquidity_wow > 0 %}#34d399{% else %}#f87171{% endif %};">
                {{ "%+.0f"|format(net_liquidity_wow) }}B WoW
              </div>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            {% endif %}
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td>
  </tr>

  <!-- ── Section 1: 유동성 공급 측 ──────────────────────────── -->
  <tr>
    <td style="background:#131929;padding:24px 32px 16px;">
      <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#60a5fa;letter-spacing:1px;
                  text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px;border-bottom:1px solid #1e2d45;
                  padding-bottom:8px;">
        🏦 유동성 공급 측 (FRED)
      </div>

      <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
        <!-- Fed BS row -->
        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #1a2236;">
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8;width:40%;">Fed 자산 총계{% if fred.walcl_date %}<div style="font-size:10px;color:#334155;margin-top:2px;">{{ fred.walcl_date }}</div>{% endif %}</td>
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#f1f5f9;text-align:right;">
            {% if fred.walcl_b is not none %}${{ "%.0f"|format(fred.walcl_b) }}B{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:12px;text-align:right;width:100px;">
            {% if fred.walcl_wow is not none %}
            <span style="color:{% if fred.walcl_wow > 0 %}#34d399{% else %}#f87171{% endif %};">
              {{ "%+.0f"|format(fred.walcl_wow) }}B WoW
            </span>
            {% endif %}
          </td>
        </tr>
        <!-- TGA row -->
        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #1a2236;">
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8;">TGA 잔고{% if fred.tga_date %}<div style="font-size:10px;color:#334155;margin-top:2px;">{{ fred.tga_date }}</div>{% endif %}</td>
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#f1f5f9;text-align:right;">
            {% if fred.tga_b is not none %}${{ "%.0f"|format(fred.tga_b) }}B{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:12px;text-align:right;">
            {% if fred.tga_wow is not none %}
            <span style="color:{% if fred.tga_wow < 0 %}#34d399{% else %}#f87171{% endif %};">
              {{ "%+.0f"|format(fred.tga_wow) }}B WoW
            </span>
            {% endif %}
          </td>
        </tr>
        <!-- RRP row -->
        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #1a2236;">
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8;">RRP 잔고{% if fred.rrp_date %}<div style="font-size:10px;color:#334155;margin-top:2px;">{{ fred.rrp_date }}</div>{% endif %}</td>
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#f1f5f9;text-align:right;">
            {% if fred.rrp_b is not none %}${{ "%.1f"|format(fred.rrp_b) }}B{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:12px;text-align:right;">
            {% if fred.rrp_wow is not none %}
            <span style="color:{% if fred.rrp_wow < 0 %}#34d399{% else %}#f87171{% endif %};">
              {{ "%+.1f"|format(fred.rrp_wow) }}B WoW
            </span>
            {% endif %}
          </td>
        </tr>
        <!-- MMF rows -->
        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #1a2236;">
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8;">MMF 잔고 (주간추적){% if fred.mmf_weekly_date %}<div style="font-size:10px;color:#334155;margin-top:2px;">{{ fred.mmf_weekly_date }}</div>{% endif %}</td>
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#f1f5f9;text-align:right;">
            {% if fred.mmf_weekly_b is not none %}${{ "%.0f"|format(fred.mmf_weekly_b) }}B{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:12px;text-align:right;">
            {% if fred.mmf_flow_b is not none %}
            <span style="color:{% if fred.mmf_flow_b > 0 %}#f87171{% else %}#34d399{% endif %};">
              순유출입 {{ "%+.1f"|format(fred.mmf_flow_b) }}B
            </span>
            {% endif %}
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #1a2236;">
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8;">MMF 전체 (분기){% if fred.mmf_total_date %}<div style="font-size:10px;color:#334155;margin-top:2px;">{{ fred.mmf_total_date }}</div>{% endif %}</td>
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#f1f5f9;text-align:right;" colspan="2">
            {% if fred.mmf_total_b is not none %}${{ "%.0f"|format(fred.mmf_total_b) }}B{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
        </tr>
        <!-- Yield curve -->
        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #1a2236;">
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8;">2s10s 스프레드{% if fred.yield_2s10s_date %}<div style="font-size:10px;color:#334155;margin-top:2px;">{{ fred.yield_2s10s_date }}</div>{% endif %}</td>
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;text-align:right;
                     color:{% if fred.yield_2s10s_b is not none and fred.yield_2s10s_b > 0 %}#34d399{% else %}#f87171{% endif %};">
            {% if fred.yield_2s10s_b is not none %}{{ "%+.2f"|format(fred.yield_2s10s_b) }}%{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:12px;color:#64748b;text-align:right;">
            2Y {{ "%.2f"|format(fred.dgs2_b) if fred.dgs2_b is not none else "—" }}%
            / 10Y {{ "%.2f"|format(fred.dgs10_b) if fred.dgs10_b is not none else "—" }}%
          </td>
        </tr>
        <!-- HY Spread -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8;">HY 크레딧 스프레드{% if fred.hy_spread_date %}<div style="font-size:10px;color:#334155;margin-top:2px;">{{ fred.hy_spread_date }}</div>{% endif %}</td>
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;text-align:right;
                     color:{% if fred.hy_spread_b is not none and fred.hy_spread_b < 4 %}#34d399{% elif fred.hy_spread_b is not none and fred.hy_spread_b > 6 %}#f87171{% else %}#f1f5f9{% endif %};">
            {% if fred.hy_spread_b is not none %}{{ "%.2f"|format(fred.hy_spread_b) }}%{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:12px;color:#64748b;text-align:right;">
            {% if fred.hy_spread_b is not none %}
              {% if fred.hy_spread_b < 3.5 %}극도 타이트{% elif fred.hy_spread_b < 5 %}정상{% else %}확대{% endif %}
            {% endif %}
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      {% if charts and charts.liquidity %}
      <div style="margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:6px;font-size:11px;color:#475569;">유동성 공급 측 (2년)</div>
      <img src="data:image/png;base64,{{ charts.liquidity }}"
           style="width:100%;max-width:556px;display:block;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:12px;" alt="Liquidity Chart">
      {% endif %}
      {% if charts and charts.mmf %}
      <div style="margin-bottom:6px;font-size:11px;color:#475569;">MMF 자금 동향</div>
      <img src="data:image/png;base64,{{ charts.mmf }}"
           style="width:100%;max-width:556px;display:block;border-radius:6px;" alt="MMF Chart">
      {% endif %}
    </td>
  </tr>

  <!-- ── Section 2: 흐름 신호 (통화) ────────────────────────── -->
  <tr>
    <td style="background:#0f1520;padding:20px 32px 16px;border-top:1px solid #1a2236;">
      {%- set _ns = namespace(date="") -%}
      {%- for _, d in currencies.items() -%}{%- if _ns.date == "" and "error" not in d and d.date -%}{%- set _ns.date = d.date -%}{%- endif -%}{%- endfor -%}
      <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#a78bfa;letter-spacing:1px;
                  text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px;border-bottom:1px solid #1e2d45;
                  padding-bottom:8px;">
        💱 흐름 신호 (통화){% if _ns.date %}<span style="float:right;font-size:10px;color:#475569;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0;text-transform:none;">기준 {{ _ns.date }}</span>{% endif %}
      </div>
      <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #1a2236;">
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;font-weight:600;">통화</td>
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;text-align:right;">현재</td>
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;text-align:right;">1일</td>
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;text-align:right;">1주</td>
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;text-align:right;">1개월</td>
        </tr>
        {% for name, d in currencies.items() %}
        {% if "error" not in d %}
        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #131929;">
          <td style="padding:7px 0;font-size:13px;color:#cbd5e1;">{{ name }}</td>
          <td style="padding:7px 0;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#f1f5f9;text-align:right;">
            {{ "%.4g"|format(d.last) }}
          </td>
          <td style="padding:7px 0;font-size:12px;text-align:right;
                     color:{% if d.pct_1d is not none and d.pct_1d > 0 %}#34d399{% elif d.pct_1d is not none %}#f87171{% else %}#64748b{% endif %};">
            {% if d.pct_1d is not none %}{{ "%+.2f"|format(d.pct_1d) }}%{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
          <td style="padding:7px 0;font-size:12px;text-align:right;
                     color:{% if d.pct_1w is not none and d.pct_1w > 0 %}#34d399{% elif d.pct_1w is not none %}#f87171{% else %}#64748b{% endif %};">
            {% if d.pct_1w is not none %}{{ "%+.2f"|format(d.pct_1w) }}%{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
          <td style="padding:7px 0;font-size:12px;text-align:right;
                     color:{% if d.pct_1m is not none and d.pct_1m > 0 %}#34d399{% elif d.pct_1m is not none %}#f87171{% else %}#64748b{% endif %};">
            {% if d.pct_1m is not none %}{{ "%+.2f"|format(d.pct_1m) }}%{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
        </tr>
        {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </table>

      {% if charts and charts.currencies %}
      <div style="margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:6px;font-size:11px;color:#475569;">통화 흐름 신호 (1년)</div>
      <img src="data:image/png;base64,{{ charts.currencies }}"
           style="width:100%;max-width:556px;display:block;border-radius:6px;" alt="Currency Chart">
      {% endif %}
    </td>
  </tr>

  <!-- ── Section 3: 도착지 신호 ──────────────────────────────── -->
  <tr>
    <td style="background:#131929;padding:20px 32px 16px;border-top:1px solid #1a2236;">
      {%- set _ns = namespace(date="") -%}
      {%- for _, d in destinations.items() -%}{%- if _ns.date == "" and "error" not in d and d.date -%}{%- set _ns.date = d.date -%}{%- endif -%}{%- endfor -%}
      <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#fb923c;letter-spacing:1px;
                  text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px;border-bottom:1px solid #1e2d45;
                  padding-bottom:8px;">
        🏁 도착지 신호 (자산){% if _ns.date %}<span style="float:right;font-size:10px;color:#475569;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0;text-transform:none;">기준 {{ _ns.date }}</span>{% endif %}
      </div>
      <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #1a2236;">
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;font-weight:600;">자산</td>
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;text-align:right;">현재가</td>
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;text-align:right;">1일</td>
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;text-align:right;">1주</td>
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;text-align:right;">1개월</td>
        </tr>
        {% for name, d in destinations.items() %}
        {% if "error" not in d %}
        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #0f1520;">
          <td style="padding:7px 0;font-size:13px;color:#cbd5e1;">{{ name }}</td>
          <td style="padding:7px 0;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#f1f5f9;text-align:right;">
            {% if d.last >= 1000 %}{{ "%.0f"|format(d.last) }}
            {% elif d.last >= 10 %}{{ "%.2f"|format(d.last) }}
            {% else %}{{ "%.4f"|format(d.last) }}
            {% endif %}
          </td>
          <td style="padding:7px 0;font-size:12px;text-align:right;
                     color:{% if d.pct_1d is not none and d.pct_1d > 0 %}#34d399{% elif d.pct_1d is not none %}#f87171{% else %}#64748b{% endif %};">
            {% if d.pct_1d is not none %}{{ "%+.2f"|format(d.pct_1d) }}%{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
          <td style="padding:7px 0;font-size:12px;text-align:right;
                     color:{% if d.pct_1w is not none and d.pct_1w > 0 %}#34d399{% elif d.pct_1w is not none %}#f87171{% else %}#64748b{% endif %};">
            {% if d.pct_1w is not none %}{{ "%+.2f"|format(d.pct_1w) }}%{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
          <td style="padding:7px 0;font-size:12px;text-align:right;
                     color:{% if d.pct_1m is not none and d.pct_1m > 0 %}#34d399{% elif d.pct_1m is not none %}#f87171{% else %}#64748b{% endif %};">
            {% if d.pct_1m is not none %}{{ "%+.2f"|format(d.pct_1m) }}%{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
        </tr>
        {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </table>

      {% if charts and charts.destinations %}
      <div style="margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:6px;font-size:11px;color:#475569;">도착지 자산 (1년, 기준=100)</div>
      <img src="data:image/png;base64,{{ charts.destinations }}"
           style="width:100%;max-width:556px;display:block;border-radius:6px;" alt="Destination Chart">
      {% endif %}
    </td>
  </tr>

  <!-- ── Section 4: 섹터 ETF ─────────────────────────────────── -->
  {% if sectors %}
  <tr>
    <td style="background:#131929;padding:20px 32px 16px;border-top:1px solid #1a2236;">
      {%- set _ns = namespace(date="") -%}
      {%- for _, d in sectors.items() -%}{%- if _ns.date == "" and "error" not in d and d.date -%}{%- set _ns.date = d.date -%}{%- endif -%}{%- endfor -%}
      <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#22d3ee;letter-spacing:1px;
                  text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px;border-bottom:1px solid #1e2d45;
                  padding-bottom:8px;">
        🔄 섹터 순환 (S&amp;P 500 GICS){% if _ns.date %}<span style="float:right;font-size:10px;color:#475569;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0;text-transform:none;">기준 {{ _ns.date }}</span>{% endif %}
      </div>
      <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #1a2236;">
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;font-weight:600;width:42%;">섹터</td>
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#64748b;text-align:right;">1주</td>
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#64748b;text-align:right;">1달</td>
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#64748b;text-align:right;">3달</td>
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#64748b;text-align:right;">1년</td>
        </tr>
        {% for name, d in sectors.items() %}
        {% if "error" not in d %}
        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #0f1520;">
          <td style="padding:6px 0;font-size:12px;color:#cbd5e1;">{{ name }}</td>
          {# 1주 #}
          <td style="padding:6px 0;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;text-align:right;
                     color:{% if d.pct_1w is not none and d.pct_1w > 0 %}#34d399{% elif d.pct_1w is not none %}#f87171{% else %}#64748b{% endif %};">
            {% if d.pct_1w is not none %}{{ "%+.1f"|format(d.pct_1w) }}%{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
          {# 1달 #}
          <td style="padding:6px 0;font-size:12px;text-align:right;
                     color:{% if d.pct_1m is not none and d.pct_1m > 0 %}#34d399{% elif d.pct_1m is not none %}#f87171{% else %}#64748b{% endif %};">
            {% if d.pct_1m is not none %}{{ "%+.1f"|format(d.pct_1m) }}%{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
          {# 3달 #}
          <td style="padding:6px 0;font-size:12px;text-align:right;
                     color:{% if d.pct_3m is not none and d.pct_3m > 0 %}#34d399{% elif d.pct_3m is not none %}#f87171{% else %}#64748b{% endif %};">
            {% if d.pct_3m is not none %}{{ "%+.1f"|format(d.pct_3m) }}%{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
          {# 1년 #}
          <td style="padding:6px 0;font-size:12px;text-align:right;
                     color:{% if d.pct_1y is not none and d.pct_1y > 0 %}#34d399{% elif d.pct_1y is not none %}#f87171{% else %}#64748b{% endif %};">
            {% if d.pct_1y is not none %}{{ "%+.1f"|format(d.pct_1y) }}%{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
        </tr>
        {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </table>

      {% if charts and charts.sectors %}
      <div style="margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:6px;font-size:11px;color:#475569;">섹터 순환 (1년 추세 + 1주 성과)</div>
      <img src="data:image/png;base64,{{ charts.sectors }}"
           style="width:100%;max-width:556px;display:block;border-radius:6px;" alt="Sector Chart">
      {% endif %}
    </td>
  </tr>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- ── Section 5: 크립토 ──────────────────────────────────── -->
  {% if crypto and (crypto.btc or crypto.eth) %}
  <tr>
    <td style="background:#0f1520;padding:20px 32px 16px;border-top:1px solid #1a2236;">
      <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#f7931a;letter-spacing:1px;
                  text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px;border-bottom:1px solid #1e2d45;
                  padding-bottom:8px;">
        ₿ 크립토 시장{% if crypto.btc and crypto.btc.date %}<span style="float:right;font-size:10px;color:#475569;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0;text-transform:none;">기준 {{ crypto.btc.date }}</span>{% endif %}
      </div>

      <!-- BTC / ETH 가격 테이블 -->
      <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:12px;">
        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #1a2236;">
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;font-weight:600;width:24%;">자산</td>
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;text-align:right;">현재가</td>
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;text-align:right;">1일</td>
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;text-align:right;">1주</td>
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;text-align:right;">1달</td>
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;text-align:right;">3달</td>
          <td style="padding:4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;text-align:right;">1년</td>
        </tr>

        {# BTC row #}
        {% if crypto.btc and "error" not in crypto.btc %}
        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #131929;">
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#f7931a;">₿ Bitcoin</td>
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#f1f5f9;text-align:right;">
            ${{ "{:,.0f}".format(crypto.btc.price) }}
          </td>
          {% for k in ["pct_1d", "pct_1w", "pct_1m", "pct_3m", "pct_1y"] %}
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:12px;text-align:right;
                     color:{% if crypto.btc[k] is not none and crypto.btc[k] > 0 %}#34d399{% elif crypto.btc[k] is not none %}#f87171{% else %}#64748b{% endif %};">
            {% if crypto.btc[k] is not none %}{{ "%+.1f"|format(crypto.btc[k]) }}%{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
          {% endfor %}
        </tr>
        {% endif %}

        {# ETH row #}
        {% if crypto.eth and "error" not in crypto.eth %}
        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #131929;">
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#627eea;">⟠ Ethereum</td>
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#f1f5f9;text-align:right;">
            ${{ "{:,.0f}".format(crypto.eth.price) }}
          </td>
          {% for k in ["pct_1d", "pct_1w", "pct_1m", "pct_3m", "pct_1y"] %}
          <td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:12px;text-align:right;
                     color:{% if crypto.eth[k] is not none and crypto.eth[k] > 0 %}#34d399{% elif crypto.eth[k] is not none %}#f87171{% else %}#64748b{% endif %};">
            {% if crypto.eth[k] is not none %}{{ "%+.1f"|format(crypto.eth[k]) }}%{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
          {% endfor %}
        </tr>
        {% endif %}
      </table>

      <!-- DeFi TVL 요약 (가로 3칸) -->
      {% if crypto.eth_tvl_b is not none or crypto.l2_tvl_b is not none or crypto.total_tvl_b is not none %}
      <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:10px;">
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:8px 12px;background:#131929;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;width:33%;">
            <div style="font-size:10px;color:#64748b;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:4px;">ETH DeFi TVL</div>
            <div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#627eea;">
              {% if crypto.eth_tvl_b is not none %}${{ crypto.eth_tvl_b }}B{% else %}—{% endif %}
            </div>
          </td>
          <td width="8"></td>
          <td style="padding:8px 12px;background:#131929;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;width:33%;">
            <div style="font-size:10px;color:#64748b;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:4px;">L2 TVL 합계</div>
            <div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#22d3ee;">
              {% if crypto.l2_tvl_b is not none %}${{ crypto.l2_tvl_b }}B{% else %}—{% endif %}
            </div>
          </td>
          <td width="8"></td>
          <td style="padding:8px 12px;background:#131929;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;width:33%;">
            <div style="font-size:10px;color:#64748b;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:4px;">전체 DeFi TVL</div>
            <div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#34d399;">
              {% if crypto.total_tvl_b is not none %}${{ "{:,.0f}".format(crypto.total_tvl_b) }}B{% else %}—{% endif %}
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      {% endif %}

      <!-- 마켓 심리 지표 (BTC 도미넌스 / ETH/BTC / 공포탐욕) -->
      {% if crypto.btc_dominance is not none or crypto.eth_btc_ratio is not none or crypto.fear_greed %}
      <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:8px 12px;background:#131929;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;width:33%;">
            <div style="font-size:10px;color:#64748b;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:4px;">BTC 도미넌스</div>
            <div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#f7931a;">
              {% if crypto.btc_dominance is not none %}{{ "%.1f"|format(crypto.btc_dominance) }}%{% else %}—{% endif %}
            </div>
          </td>
          <td width="8"></td>
          <td style="padding:8px 12px;background:#131929;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;width:33%;">
            <div style="font-size:10px;color:#64748b;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:4px;">ETH / BTC</div>
            <div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#627eea;">
              {% if crypto.eth_btc_ratio is not none %}{{ "%.5f"|format(crypto.eth_btc_ratio) }}{% else %}—{% endif %}
            </div>
          </td>
          <td width="8"></td>
          <td style="padding:8px 12px;background:#131929;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;width:33%;">
            <div style="font-size:10px;color:#64748b;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:4px;">공포 &amp; 탐욕</div>
            {% if crypto.fear_greed %}
            {%- set fg = crypto.fear_greed.value -%}
            <div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;
                        color:{% if fg <= 24 %}#f87171{% elif fg <= 49 %}#fb923c{% elif fg <= 74 %}#34d399{% else %}#4ade80{% endif %};">
              {{ fg }}
            </div>
            <div style="font-size:10px;color:#64748b;margin-top:2px;">{{ crypto.fear_greed.label }}</div>
            {% else %}
            <div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#64748b;">—</div>
            {% endif %}
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      {% endif %}

      {% if charts and charts.crypto_price %}
      <div style="margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:6px;font-size:11px;color:#475569;">BTC / ETH 가격 추이 (1년, 기준=100)</div>
      <img src="data:image/png;base64,{{ charts.crypto_price }}"
           style="width:100%;max-width:556px;display:block;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:12px;" alt="Crypto Price Chart">
      {% endif %}
      {% if charts and charts.eth_tvl %}
      <div style="margin-bottom:6px;font-size:11px;color:#475569;">ETH DeFi TVL (1년)</div>
      <img src="data:image/png;base64,{{ charts.eth_tvl }}"
           style="width:100%;max-width:556px;display:block;border-radius:6px;" alt="ETH TVL Chart">
      {% endif %}

    </td>
  </tr>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- ── Footer ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <tr>
    <td style="background:#0a0f1a;border-radius:0 0 12px 12px;padding:16px 32px;
               border-top:1px solid #1a2236;">
      <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
        <tr>
          <td style="font-size:10px;color:#334155;line-height:1.6;">
            본 리포트는 투자 참고용이며 투자 권유가 아닙니다. 투자 결정은 본인 판단과 책임 하에 이루어져야 합니다.
            FRED 데이터 기준일은 발표 주기에 따라 최대 7~10일 지연될 수 있습니다.
          </td>
          <td align="right" style="font-size:10px;color:#1e3a5f;white-space:nowrap;padding-left:16px;">
            주식부자프로젝트
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td>
  </tr>

</table>
<!-- /Wrapper -->

</td></tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>
